# CommonMark inline-level converter in C

> Implement a CommonMark Markdown-to-HTML converter in C from scratch, scoped to inline-level constructs (emphasis, code spans, links, images, autolinks, raw HTML, entities, escapes, line breaks). Reads stdin, writes HTML to stdout, must compile via make and produce /app/workspace/md2html.

---

