| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Difficulty | hard |
| Category | programming |
| Agent Timeout | 7200s |
| Verifier Timeout | 600s |
| Internet Access | Disabled |
| CPUs / Memory | 2 / 4096 MB |

